sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    %% ========================================
    %% Flow 1: Fine-Tuning Pipeline (LoRA/SFT/OSFT)
    %% ========================================

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
    Note over HFHub,ModelRegistry: Flow 1: Fine-Tuning Pipeline (LoRA/SFT/OSFT)

    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DatasetDL as dataset_download<br/>Component
    participant PVC as Shared PVC<br/>(50Gi)
    participant Trainer as train_model<br/>(Kubeflow Trainer)
    participant Evaluator as universal_llm_evaluator<br/>(lm-eval + vLLM)
    participant ModelRegistry as Model Registry<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    DatasetDL->>HFHub: GET datasets<br/>Auth: Bearer HF_TOKEN<br/>TLS 1.2+
    HFHub-->>DatasetDL: Dataset (JSONL)
    DatasetDL->>S3: GET training data<br/>Auth: AWS Signature V4<br/>TLS 1.2+
    S3-->>DatasetDL: CSV/JSONL files
    DatasetDL->>PVC: Write train/eval splits<br/>Filesystem
    PVC->>Trainer: Read training data<br/>Filesystem
    Note over Trainer: LoRA (Unsloth) / SFT (InstructLab) / OSFT (mini-trainer)<br/>GPU accelerated via TrainJob CRD
    Trainer->>PVC: Write model artifacts<br/>Filesystem
    PVC->>Evaluator: Read model + eval data<br/>Filesystem
    Note over Evaluator: lm-eval harness with vLLM backend
    Evaluator-->>Evaluator: Evaluation metrics (KFP Artifact)
    Evaluator->>ModelRegistry: POST model registration<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount<br/>plaintext (cluster-internal)
    end

    %% ========================================
    %% Flow 2: AutoML Tabular Pipeline
    %% ========================================

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
    Note over S3,Leaderboard: Flow 2: AutoML Tabular/Timeseries Pipeline

    participant DataLoader as data_loader<br/>(odh-automl image)
    participant AutoGluon as models_training<br/>(AutoGluon)
    participant Leaderboard as leaderboard_evaluation<br/>(AutoGluon)

    DataLoader->>S3: GET training CSV<br/>Auth: AWS Signature V4<br/>TLS 1.2+
    S3-->>DataLoader: CSV data files
    DataLoader->>PVC: Write train/test splits<br/>Filesystem
    PVC->>AutoGluon: Read data splits<br/>Filesystem
    Note over AutoGluon: AutoGluon TabularPredictor / TimeSeriesPredictor<br/>Automated model selection + training
    AutoGluon->>PVC: Write trained models<br/>Filesystem
    PVC->>Leaderboard: Read models + test data<br/>Filesystem
    Note over Leaderboard: Generates HTML leaderboard (KFP Artifact)
    end

    %% ========================================
    %% Flow 3: AutoRAG Optimization Pipeline
    %% ========================================

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
    Note over S3,Milvus: Flow 3: AutoRAG Optimization Pipeline

    participant Discovery as documents_discovery<br/>(odh-autorag image)
    participant Extraction as text_extraction<br/>(docling)
    participant Indexing as documents_indexing<br/>(OGX client)
    participant OGXAPI as OGX API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Milvus as Milvus Vector DB<br/>19530/TCP gRPC
    participant RAGOptim as rag_templates_optimization<br/>(ai4rag)
    participant ResponsesBuilder as prepare_responses<br/>api_requests

    Discovery->>S3: LIST objects (documents)<br/>Auth: AWS Signature V4<br/>TLS 1.2+
    S3-->>Discovery: Document manifest
    Note over Discovery: Produces JSON manifest (KFP Artifact)
    Extraction->>S3: GET documents (PDF, DOCX, PPTX)<br/>Auth: AWS Signature V4<br/>TLS 1.2+
    S3-->>Extraction: Raw documents
    Note over Extraction: docling extracts text to Markdown
    Extraction-->>Extraction: Markdown files (KFP Artifact)
    Indexing->>OGXAPI: POST embeddings<br/>Auth: Bearer OGX_CLIENT_API_KEY<br/>TLS 1.2+
    OGXAPI->>Milvus: Store vectors<br/>gRPC/19530<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Milvus-->>OGXAPI: Index confirmation
    OGXAPI-->>Indexing: Indexing complete
    Note over RAGOptim: Iterative RAG template optimization
    RAGOptim->>OGXAPI: POST evaluate patterns<br/>Auth: Bearer OGX_CLIENT_API_KEY<br/>TLS 1.2+
    OGXAPI-->>RAGOptim: Evaluation results
    Note over RAGOptim: Produces optimized pattern.json (KFP Artifact)
    RAGOptim->>ResponsesBuilder: Optimized RAG patterns
    Note over ResponsesBuilder: Generates OGX /v1/responses request bodies
    end

    %% ========================================
    %% Flow 4: SDG Pipeline
    %% ========================================

    rect rgb(255, 240, 255)
    Note over InputData,SDGOutput: Flow 4: SDG (Synthetic Data Generation) Pipeline

    participant InputData as Input Dataset<br/>(Artifact/PVC)
    participant SDG as sdg component<br/>(sdg-hub + LiteLLM)
    participant LLMAPI as LLM API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant SDGOutput as Output JSONL<br/>(Artifact + PVC)

    InputData->>SDG: Read input data<br/>Filesystem/KFP Artifact
    SDG->>LLMAPI: POST generate synthetic data<br/>Auth: Bearer LLM_API_KEY<br/>TLS 1.2+
    LLMAPI-->>SDG: Generated synthetic samples
    SDG->>SDGOutput: Write JSONL output<br/>Filesystem/KFP Artifact
    end
